name: BASKET CASE NAILS!!!
description:
This hipster design is unlike any other, almost an optical illusion perching on your finger tips, catching the eye of and bemusing strangers...
Alternating nude and pastel blue with the black triangle design on top - high quality polish and uhhh-mazing top coat for no chip chip chipping, you can rest assured.
Glue is not included.
If you wanna have a gander at these beauts any closer, let me know and I can get some more photos sent on over to you!

name: FLURO-ANIMAL NAILS!!!
description:
Now are these nails going to be known as Tigepard or Leopiger because this mix of tiger and leopard print is beyond naming!
A combination of both fluorescent pink and orange with black animal markings these will definitely not go unnoticed!
And never fear this smashing print is here to stay with super-fast topcoat and high quality polish, it ain't budging.
Glue is not included.
MORE PICS, MESSAGE MOI :)

name: GALAXY NAILS!!!
description:
These celestial beauts have popped on down to earth for a visit and are crying out to reside on the tips of your lovely fingers.
Dipped with glitter, these acrylic lovelies are not planning on chipping (fabby top coat and polish) and have been filed into a super-flattering almond shape.
8 of the nails are purple with a mix of black and silver glitter and the ring finger nails have something a little special going on with a navy background - just to mix things up a little!
Does not include nail glue.
MORE PHOTOS? MESSAGE ME UP :)

name: TUXEDO NAILS!!!
description:
These nails really have made an effort, all dressed up in tuxedo's how can you not fall in love with the little cuties?
Acrylic false nails pre-filed and painted with high quality polish and LASHINGS of super-hard top coat (these beauties are tough cookies)
Does not include nail glue.
If ya need any more photos feel free to drop me a message and I'll send some on over you you :) 
(the thumb nail is also wearing a tuxedo!)

name: AZTEC NAILS!!!
description:
These nails are about as cool and hipster as you can get, with a snazzy black aztec design on a green background, EVERYONE is bound to be well jel of your nails.
They are acrylic nails pre-filed into an almond shape and painted with high quality polish (and a smacking of top coat to avoid chippage!)
Glue is not included with these nails.
if you would like more photos drop me an email ;)
